  "instructions": [
    "Heat olive oil in a pan over medium heat.",
    "Add onions and garlic, sautéing until translucent, about 5 minutes.",
    "Stir in bell peppers and cook for another 3-4 minutes or until slightly softened.",
    "Juice the limes into the pan along with their seeds and membranes. Add salt and pepper to taste.",
    "Fold spinach leaves into the mixture, stirring gently to wilt them.",
    "If desired, add a pinch of diastatic barley malt syrup for sweetness without adding extra sugar.",
